trans-unit.source: Provides a control array of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: 提供 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.PrintDialog" /> 控制項的控制項陣列。

trans-unit.source: The `PrintDialogArray` class provides an equivalent for the run-time functionality of a Visual Basic 6.0 `PrintDialog` array.
trans-unit.target: `PrintDialogArray`類別提供對等項目執行階段功能的 Visual Basic 6.0`PrintDialog`陣列。

trans-unit.source: It does not provide the design-time features of a Visual Basic 6.0 control array.
trans-unit.target: 它不提供 Visual Basic 6.0 控制項陣列的設計階段功能。

trans-unit.target: 只有當 Visual Basic 6.0 程式碼模型與 [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] 實作有顯著差異時，才需要這些項目。
